<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/35846600.259286/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL=
2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDUtMjAvdGhlLWVuZGxlc3Mtc2hyaW1wLWludmVzdGlnYXRpb24_Y21w=
