nst Greenlight, which had claimed Greenlight defamed him by telling people =
he=C2=A0<em>wasn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0</em>the head of macro. And now Greenlight =
has=C2=A0filed a new lawsuit, which claims that Fishback is defaming Greenl=
ight by telling people that he was. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/35846600.259286/aHR0cHM6Ly9hc3NldHMuYndieC5pby9kb2N1bWVud=
