dth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgro=
und-color: #ccc;">Here is the complaint</a>; a sample:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fishback also used false statements in his fri=
volous lawsuit as an improper opportunity to publicly misrepresent his role=
 and performance at Greenlight by falsely claiming that he was =E2=80=9Can =
outstanding performer at Greenlight,=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9Cexcelled in his work=
,=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Cgenerated over $100 million in profits for Greenlig=
ht from the period of February 2021 to August 2023.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">None of this is true. In fact, Fishback was su=
ch a poor performer at Greenlight that Greenlight had actually decided to t=
erminate him for his lack of productivity and scheduled a meeting with him =
to do so, but he abruptly resigned when he deduced that he was about to be =
terminated. And, since he had absolutely no authority or discretion whatsoe=
ver over Greenlight=E2=80=99s macro investment portfolio, he was not respon=
sible for generating any profits, let alone =E2=80=9Cover $100 million=E2=
=80=9D of profits.</p>
