<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fishback is a fairly young person who was hire=
d at Greenlight in a somewhat unconventional=C2=A0way. (He =E2=80=9Cis a se=
lf-taught investment professional who successfully ran his own hedge fund f=
or five years,=E2=80=9D said <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/35846600.259286/aHR0cHM6Ly9hc3NldHMuYndieC5pby9kb2N1bWVudHMvdXNl=
cnMvaXFqV0hCRmRmeElVL3JHUFpEMUNmSW9aRS92MA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBdaa9711=
9" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">his lawsuit</a>, and =E2=80=9Cpersonally consulted Greenlight=
=E2=80=99s founder and CEO, David Einhorn, on macro investing beginning in =
early April 2019,=E2=80=9D before actually being hired at Greenlight in 202=
1.) He worked there as an analyst covering macro, and=C2=A0he claims that h=
e is responsible for the performance of Greenlight=E2=80=99s macro portfoli=
o.=C2=A0Greenlight says that in fact Einhorn was the only person with inves=
ting discretion, Fishback just researched ideas for Einhorn, and in fact he=
 didn=E2=80=99t do a very good job, in part because he=C2=A0was distracted =
by his extracurricular activity of=C2=A0running a high school debate progra=
m. It is hard to convey, in a legal complaint, that someone was not a very =
good hedge fund analyst, but Greenlight tries:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Throughout 2022, Greenlight provided Fishback =
with clear notice that he was not meeting expectations. For instance, on Ap=
ril 19, 2022, Mr. Einhorn expressed disappointment with the lack of substan=
ce in an assignment that Fishback had taken six days to complete and expres=
sed to him that he thought Fishback=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Cwork, as shown, coul=
d be replicated in about 30<br />minutes.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In Fishback=E2=80=99s formal year-end performa=
nce assessment for 2022, Greenlight also communicated to him that =E2=80=9C=
<strong>[w]hen projects are assigned by David to James, they often don=E2=
=80=99t get evaluated in a timely manner and sometimes not at all</strong>=
=E2=80=9D (emphasis added). The assessment continued that: =E2=80=9C[t]o su=
mmarize: we aren=E2=80=99t sure whether the lack of work is because (a) Jam=
es disagrees with the topic, so he refuses to indulge David=E2=80=99s reque=
st in a passive/aggressive way, (b) James isn=E2=80=99t capable of investig=
ating these types of questions, or (c) James isn=E2=80=99t committing enoug=
h hours to his work at Greenlight.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And Einhorn emailed him in May 2023:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We genuinely doubt you are working=
 as a full time employee. We don=E2=80=99t have punch clocks and you work r=
emotely. So, the burden of proof is on you. And, it looks like your side gi=
g is cutting into Greenlight. In fact, it really doesn=E2=80=99t appear to =
me that you are doing any meaningful amount of work for Greenlight. If I di=
dn=E2=80=99t like you, I=E2=80=99d fire you now. But, you are on very, very=
 thin ice.=C2=A0</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And here is a tantalizing project:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Greenlight=E2=80=99s patience with Fishback fi=
nally ran out in late July 2023. On July 26, 2023, Fishback submitted a dra=
ft essay (the =E2=80=9CJelly Donut Assignment=E2=80=9D) to Mr. Einhorn that=
 he had been assigned to write in February 2023. After many delays, the dra=
ft essay was finally supposed to be delivered on July 24, 2023. Despite it =
being two days beyond the most recent deadline, and despite Fishback have h=
aving had months to complete the Jelly Donut Assignment, the draft essay ap=
peared to reflect only a few hours of effort</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">After receiving the Jelly Donut Assignment on =
July 26, and determining that it did not reflect a substantial amount of wo=
rk, Greenlight reviewed its computer system and discovered that Fishback ha=
d almost no work files saved on Greenlight=E2=80=99s network drive, and had=
