<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Moreover, since this review revealed that virt=
ually none of Fishback=E2=80=99s work had been saved on Greenlight=E2=80=99=
s network drive, Fishback must either have been saving his Greenlight work =
files=E2=80=94which would have included a vast amount of Confidential Infor=
mation=E2=80=94on his personal devices, in direct violation of Greenlight=
=E2=80=99s policies and his Employment Agreement, or he did not do any mean=
ingful work during his entire tenure at Greenlight.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Casual Googling suggests that David Einhorn re=
ally likes <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/3584660=
