<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And then he went around telling everyone he wa=
s the =E2=80=9Chead of macro.=E2=80=9D In his lawsuit, Fishback proposed tw=
o bits of evidence for that: That title appeared on his bio at some confere=
nce appearances, and he had a screenshot of an email from Greenlight Chief =
Operating Officer Daniel Roitman describing him that way. Greenlight=E2=80=
=99s lawsuit disagrees:=C2=A0<em>He=C2=A0</em>gave himself the conference t=
itles, and =E2=80=9CGreenlight did not know that Fishback had even register=
ed as a speaker for the Citi Conference, let alone used the fictitious =E2=
=80=98Head of Macro=E2=80=99 title.=E2=80=9D And:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The screenshot was an email from Mr. Roitman t=
o Ms. Heather Robinson, a Senior Manager of the GLG Group on May 11, 2023 (=
the =E2=80=9CGLG Email=E2=80=9D). The email thread began with Ms. Robinson =
contacting Mr. Roitman to promote a =E2=80=9CRemote Roundtable=E2=80=9D mee=
ting her firm was hosting, and offering to =E2=80=9Csave [] a seat=E2=80=9D=
 for Greenlight. In response, Mr. Roitman asked Ms.=C2=A0Robinson to sign F=
ishback up for the meeting, which was relevant to Fishback=E2=80=99s duties=
 as a Research Analyst focused on macro positions, and introduced Fishback =
onto the email thread by informally remarking that he is =E2=80=9Cour head =
of macro.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">To be clear, Mr. Roitman was not stating that =
this was his formal title, as is obvious from the context and lack of a pro=
per noun. The Remote Roundtable was a GLG =E2=80=9CSignature Event=E2=80=9D=
 available only to senior executives (only Mr. Einhorn and Mr. Roitman were=
 invited), and Mr. Roitman exaggerated his description of Fishback so that =
GLG would allow him to attend the event.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So yeah I mean he was a=C2=A0<em>little=C2=A0<=
/em>bit head of macro, in the sense that everyone at a financial firm is th=
e head of something: Sometimes you want to inflate the importance of your a=
nalyst to get him into a meeting.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Sorry, I know this is so petty, but it gets pe=
ttier:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On January 10, 2024, Fishback emailed Greenlig=
ht and threatened to attend Greenlight=E2=80=99s 2024 Annual Partner Dinner=
.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Many of Greenlight=E2=80=99s investors, counte=
rparties, service providers and employee family members attend Greenlight=
=E2=80=99s Annual Partner Dinners. Fishback=E2=80=99s threats were obvious =
attempts to intimidate and embarrass Greenlight, and interfere with Greenli=
ght=E2=80=99s relationships with its investors, counterparties and service =
providers. When Greenlight notified Fishback that he was not permitted to a=
ttend, he insisted that he would still attempt to do so, or at a minimum, s=
tand outside the event venue and attempt to communicate with attendees.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">He didn=E2=80=99t actually do that, but it=E2=
=80=99s a funny threat. Also he said=C2=A0mean things about Greenlight in h=
is Twitter bio:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On June 2, 2024, Fishback quite ch=
ildishly changed the bio of his X account to read: =E2=80=9CPast: Head of M=
acro at Greenlight (sucks)=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9CPast: Head of Macro at Gre=
enlight (ew),=E2=80=9D as shown below.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Greenlight also says:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Overall, Fishback seems to have ac=
complished his goal of generating the publicity he sought. Fishback=E2=80=
=99s posts themselves were widely viewed, with some receiving more than one=
 million views. Major media outlets covered the =E2=80=9Cdispute=E2=80=9D t=
hat Fishback pretextually procured, including the <em>New York Times</em>, =
<em>Business Insider</em>, <em>Yahoo Finance</em>, <em>Bloomberg</em> and <=
em>Morningstar</em>, and as a result, his wrongful statements have been pub=
lished to millions more.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yes that is going to continue happening.</p>
